{"tid":722280,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先同條女扑野，佢講左一句野令我諗左好耐","createTime":"2018-06-29T10:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T06:59:08.000Z","uid":29001,"like":1822,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"fd8c6066c46786b61e644d85fa6e4bca8cf71855","tid":722280,"uid":29001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"我地之前因為有成三個月冇得見面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n臨分開果幾晚梗係晚晚扑野到天明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啱啱接左佢返屋企 忍左三個月嘅我想將所有精力都發洩係佢身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正當搞得興高采烈嘅時候我問左佢一句<br />\n<br />\n「點呀爽唔爽呀！幾耐冇搞過野呀你個咸濕妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n佢答我一句<br />\n<br />\n「兩個月」<br />\n<br />\n係咪我時差未倒返 搞到我同佢有時間認知上嘅差異定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27455ebb4f9c3d4b49654cddfe69c98d387d2dd2","tid":722280,"uid":13541,"like":628,"dislike":5,"score":623,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"記錯sor"},{"pid":"a7889e2eb11f3ea9e90124de2dfc8cdaa5f7d591","tid":722280,"uid":34571,"like":505,"dislike":3,"score":502,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"自慰啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4100cf9a4499cdbb9b0edc65d508646f8b415f","tid":722280,"uid":119568,"like":468,"dislike":8,"score":460,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:54:23.000Z","msg":"創意: 6.5"},{"pid":"4e8670bce736236ff3ee65e2417222b4b84dedcc","tid":722280,"uid":139814,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"唔錯"},{"pid":"f3276c3f1517b4154edff18bc404d01979051960","tid":722280,"uid":77951,"like":336,"dislike":2,"score":334,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"兩個月都好過兩個禮拜"},{"pid":"0c8a0e62a76c2ebb2067584dcd8fd02384f7a2dd"